      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LEKTRA BILLS (1) was prominent throughout off a low draw but dropped right out when 6th over 410m at Horsham in a Grade 5. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. Has ability and can bounce back. PAW HADES (2) hit the frame latest (22.92) when second at Warragul in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw. Looks one of the chances. MYRNIONG STORM (8) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 5 lengths into second (22.42) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 390m. Expected to feature again. PAW GUSTO (5) was below best last time at Sale (25.05) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 9 length seventh. Has already won out of this draw.",
